[
    {
        "text": "They often say that in good times, people drink.",
        "startTime": 261,
        "endTime": 2748,
        "slowStartTime": 542,
        "slowEndTime": 4347
    },
    {
        "text": "And in bad times?",
        "startTime": 3083,
        "endTime": 3886,
        "slowStartTime": 4774,
        "slowEndTime": 6054
    },
    {
        "text": "Well, I guess people drink.",
        "startTime": 3961,
        "endTime": 6089,
        "slowStartTime": 6092,
        "slowEndTime": 9359
    },
    {
        "text": "At its simplest, it really is just barley, hops, yeast, and just water.",
        "startTime": 6628,
        "endTime": 11741,
        "slowStartTime": 10092,
        "slowEndTime": 17836
    },
    {
        "text": "But those four ingredients and a whole lot more, have increased quite a lot of late.",
        "startTime": 12233,
        "endTime": 17391,
        "slowStartTime": 18500,
        "slowEndTime": 26311
    },
    {
        "text": "Meaning that that is a little more expensive.",
        "startTime": 17769,
        "endTime": 21614,
        "slowStartTime": 26803,
        "slowEndTime": 32646
    },
    {
        "text": "Beer is the most popular alcoholic beverage in the world.",
        "startTime": 22297,
        "endTime": 25961,
        "slowStartTime": 33595,
        "slowEndTime": 39167
    },
    {
        "text": "It's a standing that has been boosted by the drink's relative affordability...",
        "startTime": 26199,
        "endTime": 30220,
        "slowStartTime": 39449,
        "slowEndTime": 45555
    },
    {
        "text": "...compared to cocktails or wine at a bar.",
        "startTime": 30347,
        "endTime": 33077,
        "slowStartTime": 45670,
        "slowEndTime": 49841
    },
    {
        "text": "But everyone from multinational brewers to small craft beer companies to pub chains...",
        "startTime": 33473,
        "endTime": 38804,
        "slowStartTime": 50359,
        "slowEndTime": 58431
    },
    {
        "text": "...has been warning about the beverage's inevitable price increase.",
        "startTime": 38937,
        "endTime": 42468,
        "slowStartTime": 58555,
        "slowEndTime": 63927
    },
    {
        "text": "In the United Kingdom, for instance, the average cost of a pint of beer...",
        "startTime": 42677,
        "endTime": 46399,
        "slowStartTime": 64165,
        "slowEndTime": 69823
    },
    {
        "text": "...has soared by 70% since the global financial crisis.",
        "startTime": 46486,
        "endTime": 50152,
        "slowStartTime": 69879,
        "slowEndTime": 75453
    },
    {
        "text": "The mean price for 568 milliliters of brew has gone from £2.30 in 2008 to £3.95 in 2022.",
        "startTime": 50401,
        "endTime": 59724,
        "slowStartTime": 75752,
        "slowEndTime": 89811
    },
    {
        "text": "The cheapest pint was found in a pub in Lancashire,...",
        "startTime": 60078,
        "endTime": 62873,
        "slowStartTime": 90267,
        "slowEndTime": 94534
    },
    {
        "text": "...in the northwest of England, at £1.79.",
        "startTime": 62960,
        "endTime": 66003,
        "slowStartTime": 94590,
        "slowEndTime": 99230
    },
    {
        "text": "The most expensive?",
        "startTime": 66158,
        "endTime": 67046,
        "slowStartTime": 99387,
        "slowEndTime": 100794
    },
    {
        "text": "London, of course, where one unnamed pub...",
        "startTime": 67233,
        "endTime": 69608,
        "slowStartTime": 101000,
        "slowEndTime": 104637
    },
    {
        "text": "...was charging a whopping £8.06 on average.",
        "startTime": 69692,
        "endTime": 73553,
        "slowStartTime": 104688,
        "slowEndTime": 110554
    },
    {
        "text": "But London is far from the priciest place to buy a beer.",
        "startTime": 73857,
        "endTime": 76995,
        "slowStartTime": 110936,
        "slowEndTime": 115717
    },
    {
        "text": "It's the seventh most expensive capital, according to one beer index,...",
        "startTime": 77264,
        "endTime": 81215,
        "slowStartTime": 116046,
        "slowEndTime": 122047
    },
    {
        "text": "...which analyzed the price of brew from local supermarkets and hotel lobbies.",
        "startTime": 81323,
        "endTime": 86178,
        "slowStartTime": 122135,
        "slowEndTime": 129492
    },
    {
        "text": "Tokyo, Bern, Paris, Beijing, Amman, and Doha,...",
        "startTime": 86393,
        "endTime": 91145,
        "slowStartTime": 129740,
        "slowEndTime": 136943
    },
    {
        "text": "...top the list of most expensive places to buy beer,...",
        "startTime": 91233,
        "endTime": 94139,
        "slowStartTime": 137000,
        "slowEndTime": 141434
    },
    {
        "text": "...with a pint costing nearly $20 in Qatar's capital.",
        "startTime": 94233,
        "endTime": 97963,
        "slowStartTime": 141500,
        "slowEndTime": 147170
    },
    {
        "text": "Why? The short answer is inflation.",
        "startTime": 98419,
        "endTime": 101033,
        "slowStartTime": 147779,
        "slowEndTime": 151775
    },
    {
        "text": "The long answer extends from the cost of raw materials...",
        "startTime": 101286,
        "endTime": 104708,
        "slowStartTime": 152079,
        "slowEndTime": 157287
    },
    {
        "text": "...to the wages of the bar staff pouring your pint.",
        "startTime": 104869,
        "endTime": 107871,
        "slowStartTime": 157454,
        "slowEndTime": 162031
    },
    {
        "text": "Just look at these charts released by Heineken, the second-largest brewer in the world.",
        "startTime": 108720,
        "endTime": 113318,
        "slowStartTime": 163230,
        "slowEndTime": 170202
    },
    {
        "text": "The costs of barley, aluminum, natural gas and paper are all going up,...",
        "startTime": 113535,
        "endTime": 118777,
        "slowStartTime": 170453,
        "slowEndTime": 178391
    },
    {
        "text": "...and Heineken told investors it’s protecting its bottom line...",
        "startTime": 118963,
        "endTime": 122344,
        "slowStartTime": 178594,
        "slowEndTime": 183741
    },
    {
        "text": "...by passing on those costs to consumers.",
        "startTime": 122431,
        "endTime": 125324,
        "slowStartTime": 183796,
        "slowEndTime": 188211
    }
]